
Ollama defaults to using port 11434. To use a custom port:

$ export OLPORT=$(python -c 'import socket; s=socket.socket(); s.bind(("", 0));
print(s.getsockname()[1]); s.close()')
$ echo $OLPORT
$ export OLLAMA_HOST=127.0.0.1:$OLPORT
$ export OLLAMA_BASE_URL="http://localhost:$OLPORT"
$ export OLLAMA_MODELS=/path/to/your/models/directory # Defaults path:
~/.ollama

Run ollama in the background
$ ollama serve &

In this instance, ollama will be using port $OLPORT


